  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The study involves the use of Retroperitoneal plane for TME for rectal anterior resection.
      Through a pilot prospective study, LR-TME will be assessed as one arm study.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      This study is based on our new suggested theory for a retro-peritoneal approach. After
      successful 2 cases of Laparoscopic extraperitoneal-TME. A pilot study for assessment of the
      feasibilty of the new approach.

      Data will be registered prospectively and the perioperative outcomes will be assessed.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
